     <div class="w-col w-col-7"> 
      <h2>LISTING INFORMATION FOR EXTERNAL WEBSITES TO LINK TO THIS SCHOLARSHIP</h2> 
      <p><strong>The DrugNews Summer 2015 Scholarship</strong> <a class="link" href="#contact"></a> </p> 
      <ul class="paragraph-list"> 
       <li class="paragraph-list-item">Must be a U.S. citizen or permanent resident currently enrolled in an undergraduate degree program with 15 hours completed</li> 
       <li class="paragraph-list-item">Must have a minimum cumulative G.P.A. of 3.0</li> 
       <li class="paragraph-list-item">Must complete an application and essay detailing why you are pursuing a career in drug research or how a family memberâ€™s drug injury has affected your education</li> 
      </ul> 
      <p>Award: $1,000 <a class="link" href="#contact"></a> </p> 
      <p>Deadline: April 30, 2015 <a class="link" href="#contact"></a> </p> 
      <p>For further information including application, please visit: <a class="link" href="#contact"></a> </p> 
      <p><strong><a href="http://www.DrugNews.net/scholarship" class="sources-link">www.DrugNews.net/scholarship</a></strong> <a class="link" href="#contact"></a> </p> 
      <p>-------------------------------------------------------- <a class="link" href="#contact"></a> </p> 
      <p><strong>The DrugNews Fall 2015 Scholarship</strong> <a class="link" href="#contact"></a> </p> 
      <ul class="paragraph-list"> 
       <li class="paragraph-list-item">Must be a U.S. citizen or permanent resident currently enrolled in an undergraduate degree program with 15 hours completed</li> 
       <li class="paragraph-list-item">Must have a minimum cumulative G.P.A. of 3.0</li> 
       <li class="paragraph-list-item">Must complete an application and essay detailing why you are pursuing a career in drug research or how a family memberâ€™s drug injury has affected your education</li> 
      </ul> 
      <p>Award: $1,000 <a class="link" href="#contact"></a> </p> 
      <p>Deadline: July 31, 2015 <a class="link" href="#contact"></a> </p> 
      <p>For further information including application, please visit: <a class="link" href="#contact"></a> </p> 
      <p><strong><a href="http://www.DrugNews.net/scholarship" class="sources-link">www.DrugNews.net/scholarship</a></strong> <a class="link" href="#contact"></a> </p> 
